{"lemma":"جَدْبِ","slug":"جَدْبِ","root":"ج.د.ب","root_slug":"ج-د-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-د-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n5185","n5188","n5191"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n5185","headword_ar":"جَدُبَ","root":"jdb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juduwbapN","text_ar":"جُدُوبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a place, S, A, K, or a country, or region, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with drought, barrenness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dearth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with drought, and dryness of the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadiba","text_ar":"جَدِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadabN","text_ar":"جَدَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (KL;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadaba","text_ar":"جَدَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ajdb","text_ar":"اجدب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A, K;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadibat","text_ar":"جَدِبَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajodabat","text_ar":"اَجْدَبَت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; both said of the earth or land ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroD","text_ar":"الاَرْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajodabati","text_ar":"اَجْدَبَتِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbilaAdu","text_ar":"البِلَادُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the countries,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regions, were affected with drought, and the prices became high"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadabahu","text_ar":"جَدَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobN","text_ar":"جَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He found fault with it; dispraised it; expressed disapprobation of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K.) So in the saying (S, A) relating to 'Omar, (A, TA,) in a trad., (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadaba Als~amara baEoda AlEi$aA='i","text_ar":"جَدَبَ السَّمَرَ بَعْدَ العِشَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEoda AlEatamapi","text_ar":"بَعْدَ العَتَمَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He expressed disapprobation of night-discourse after nightfall,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the first third of the night reckoned from the disappearance of the redness of the twilight"},{"kind":"text","text":"]."}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","K","S","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n5188","headword_ar":"جَدْبٌ","root":"jdb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Drought, barrenness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dearth; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSobN","text_ar":"خِصْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHolN","text_ar":"مَحْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, K,) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspension of rain, and dryness of the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dryness and barrenness of the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 576:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jidab~N","text_ar":"جِدَبٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a name, or subst., for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljadobN","text_ar":"الجَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaHolu","text_ar":"المَحْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as in the saying of the rájiz, cited by Sb,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"laqado xa$iytu A^ano A^araY jidab~aA\n                      \n                     \n                        fiY EaAminaA baEoda maA A^axoSab~aA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily I feared to see drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"barrenness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in this our year, after it had been abundant in herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jidab~aA","text_ar":"جِدَبَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being used for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljadobaA","text_ar":"الجَدْبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or, accord. to one reading, it is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobab~aA","text_ar":"جَدْبَبَّا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with a doubled"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"added; the change being made for the sake of the metre. (M, TA. [Respecting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoSab~aA","text_ar":"اَخْصَبَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", see 4 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xSb","text_ar":"خصب"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  Also A place, (S, A, K,) or a country, or region, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected with drought, barrenness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dearth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with drought, and dryness of the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadiybN","text_ar":"جَدِيبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaduwbN","text_ar":"جَدُوبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majoduwbN","text_ar":"مَجْدُوبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) the last derived from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"judiba","text_ar":"جُدِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"though this verb has not been used, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujodibN","text_ar":"مُجْدِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A,) of which the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAdiybu","text_ar":"مَجَادِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) You say also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN jadobN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ جَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jdb","text_ar":"جدب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. (though app. obsolete as such) and therefore applicable to a fem. subst.] (ISd, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobapN","text_ar":"جَدْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadibapN","text_ar":"جَدِبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadiybN","text_ar":"جَدِيبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaduwbN","text_ar":"جَدُوبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M, Msb) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujodibapN","text_ar":"مُجْدِبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which last the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAdiybu","text_ar":"مَجَادِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A land affected with drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (S, M, A, &c.:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDuwna juduwbN","text_ar":"اَرْضُونَ جُدُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) as though to each part were applied the term"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobN","text_ar":"جَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[used as a subst.] from which is formed the pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juduwbN","text_ar":"جُدُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobN","text_ar":"جَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is here an inf. n. used as an epithet [and therefore applicable to a pl. subst.], (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lands affected with drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S, K.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaApN jadobaA='u","text_ar":"فَلَاةٌ جَدْبَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajodabu","text_ar":"اَجْدَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A desert affected with drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is neither little nor much, neither pasture nor herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN jadiybu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ جَدِيبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljanaAbi","text_ar":"الجَنَابِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is environed by a tract affected with drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S. [But this phrase is generally used tropically, as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is ungenerous"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"illiberal"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inhospitable."},{"kind":"text","text":"See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jnb","text_ar":"جنب"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sanapN jadobapN","text_ar":"سَنَةٌ جَدْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jrz","text_ar":"جرز"},{"kind":"text","text":") and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAmN","text_ar":"عَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaduwbN","text_ar":"جَدُوبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A year of drought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaAdibu","text_ar":"اَجَادِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayobN","text_ar":"عَيْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vice, fault, defect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; (S, A, K;) a signification which may be either proper or tropical. (Er-Rághib, MF.)"}],"source_refs":["A","Msb","K","TA","S","M","ISd","Lh"]},{"entry_id":"n5191","headword_ar":"جِدَبٌّ","root":"jdb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobab~N","text_ar":"جَدْبَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadobN","text_ar":"جَدْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}